node_modules/
# tauri-build regenerates these from build.rs (AppManifest commands) + capabilities
# on every compile — derived artifacts, not source.
gen/schemas/
permissions/autogenerated/
# dist/ is committed on purpose: Homebrew builds the tray from the source tarball
# with no Node step, and tauri-build embeds dist/ at compile time. Rebuild and
# commit it whenever src-ui/ changes (the tray CI fails if it drifts).
